          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Blade/guard contacts sliding fence during bevel cuts</td>
            <td>Fence not moved clear of blade path</td>
            <td>Move sliding fence out of the way; perform a dry cut first</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

